<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #10B981; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 20px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>âœ“ Email Verified!</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @user.email.split('@').first.capitalize %>!</h2>
        
        <p>Great news! Your email address has been successfully verified.</p>
        
        <p>Your GamesReview.com account is now fully activated and ready to use. You can now:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Write and publish game reviews</li>
          <li>Rate games and share your experiences</li>
          <li>Engage with the gaming community</li>
          <li>Track your favorite games</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Thank you for being part of our gaming community!</p>
        
        <a href="<%= @profile_url %>" class="button">Visit Your Profile</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> GamesReview.com. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
